Name: {identifier}
Description: A URL-encoded string which identifies an advertisement click on a unique device

Name: {said}
Description: A unique identifier of the app in which the advertisement appeared.

Name: {package_name}
Description: Android package name for the advertised app.

Name: {timestamp}
Description: Date and time of the click in ISO8601 datetime format. Example: 2013-02-22T16:01:23Z.
